{"title":"npm/yarn/nvm proxy/registry","uid":"0199846e1d847c37ee2500de00048032","slug":"npm-yarn","date":"2023-03-20T08:12:22.000Z","updated":"2024-01-17T15:35:16.995Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/npm-yarn.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/yarn.png","content":"<p>npm stands for Node Package Manager. It’s a library and registry for JavaScript software packages. npm also has command-line tools to help you install the different packages and manage their dependencies.<br>Yarn is a package manager that doubles down as project manager. Whether you work on one-shot projects or large monorepos, as a hobbyist or an enterprise user, we’ve got you covered.</p>\n<h2 id=\"NPM\"><a href=\"#NPM\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"NPM\"></a>NPM</h2><h3 id=\"Show-config\"><a href=\"#Show-config\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Show config\"></a>Show config</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># show all config</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">npm config <span class=\"built_in\">ls</span> -l</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># or</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">npm get proxy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"Set-proxy\"><a href=\"#Set-proxy\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Set proxy\"></a>Set proxy</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm config <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> proxy=http://127.0.0.1:10809</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"Cancle-proxy\"><a href=\"#Cancle-proxy\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Cancle proxy\"></a>Cancle proxy</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm config delete proxy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"Set-registry\"><a href=\"#Set-registry\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Set registry\"></a>Set registry</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm config <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> registry https://registry.npmmirror.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"Yarn\"><a href=\"#Yarn\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Yarn\"></a>Yarn</h2><h3 id=\"Show-config-1\"><a href=\"#Show-config-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Show config\"></a>Show config</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yarn config list</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># or</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yarn config get proxy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"Set-proxy-1\"><a href=\"#Set-proxy-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Set proxy\"></a>Set proxy</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yarn config <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> proxy http://127.0.0.1:10809</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"Cancle-proxy-1\"><a href=\"#Cancle-proxy-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Cancle proxy\"></a>Cancle proxy</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yarn config delete proxy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"Set-registry-1\"><a href=\"#Set-registry-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Set registry\"></a>Set registry</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yarn config <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> registry https://registry.npmmirror.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"Nvm\"><a href=\"#Nvm\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Nvm\"></a>Nvm</h2><h3 id=\"Show-proxy\"><a href=\"#Show-proxy\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Show proxy\"></a>Show proxy</h3><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">nvm proxy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"Set-proxy-2\"><a href=\"#Set-proxy-2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Set proxy\"></a>Set proxy</h3><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">nvm proxy http://127.0.0.1:10809</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"Cancle-proxy-2\"><a href=\"#Cancle-proxy-2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Cancle proxy\"></a>Cancle proxy</h3><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">nvm proxy none</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","text":"npm stands for Node Package Manager. It’s a library and registry for JavaScript ...","permalink":"/post/npm-yarn","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":941,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"PROXY","slug":"PROXY","count":4,"path":"api/categories/PROXY.json"},{"name":"REGISTRY","slug":"PROXY/REGISTRY","count":1,"path":"api/categories/PROXY/REGISTRY.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"npm","slug":"npm","count":1,"path":"api/tags/npm.json"},{"name":"yarn","slug":"yarn","count":1,"path":"api/tags/yarn.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a cla